summary: Just a face change for Illia.
descriptionHtml:
Simple tweaking of Illia face because I was tired of putting Dwarven Helms in her invent so I wouldn\'t have to look at her.

If you like this, please endorse and check out some of my other NPC face change

-------------------
Version

1.2
Actually fixed the combat bug
1.1
Fixed a bug where she would be stuck in combat
-------------------
INSTALL

Drop .bsa and .esp file into your Data folder
 -Put at bottom of load list
 -Will conflict with mods that also change Illia\'s face

-------------------
Recommended mods

You will need these to replicate my uploaded image:

Coverwomen by MrLenski (any)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563
Covereyes by MrLenski (any)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4869
ApachiiSkyHair
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168
DIMONIZED UNP female body
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709
Void armor by Hentai
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11871

-------------------
Creds to above for their awesome textures and meshes
